customrecordcustomfield.help: Enable this for the exchange rate integration with SuiteProjects Pro. Be sure to read all documentation before enabling and make sure this is configured in SuiteProjects Pro. This is only relevant for OneWorld accounts.
customrecordcustomfield.label: Exchange Rate Integration - OneWorld

customrecordcustomfield.description:
Enable this preference if the "SuiteProjects Pro: Exchange Rates" custom script is scheduled to run at a time that is the day prior to the SuiteProjects Pro exchange rate integration. For example, if the "SuiteProjects Pro: Exchange Rates" script is scheduled to run at 10:30 PM PST and the exchange rate synchronization is scheduled to run at 12:15 AM PST, the "SuiteProjects Pro: Exchange Rates" script runs the previous day. The effective date of the exchange rates will therefore be the previous day. Enabling this preference adjusts the effective date for this scenario to give the exchange rates with an effective date that is the same as the day the SuiteProjects Pro exchange rate synchronization runs.
This preference should not be enabled if the SuiteProjects Pro exchange rate synchronization and the "SuiteProjects Pro: Exchange Rates" script are scheduled to run on the same day PST.
